<br>
Originaly this was done to stop bodies from Poofing if killed by dots / rains / poisons. Poisons and DOTs have been able to kill monsters for the last while without bodies vanishing but this has been ignored.  <br>
<br>
Its not as if this is a hard bug to duplicate,  Find a dark blue+ monster, cast rain when it has less then a bubble of health left.. Resist, resist, resist.  If mages found a way to do double damage on each rain it would be patched within hours, find a bug that stops us from using one of our main spell lines when its most needed and it stays that way because it doesnt give us any advantage.  <br>
<br>
Tested on Vallon Zek, Tallon Zek, Golums in PoV,  as well as anything else i could find (fully tashed/ malosinia'd)<br>
